  "rawText": "ii. 可数名词\n选择填空。\n( B ) 1) In his letter, Uncle Lee told us many ______ about his visit to the United States.\nA. news  B. stories  C. information  D. truth\n( C ) 2) I spent large numbers of ______ preparing for the final exams.\nA. energy  B. time  C. hours  D. strength\n( C ) 3) Many tourists from different ______ come to visit Shanghai every year.\nA. country  B. countries  C. countries  D. country’s\n( B ) 4) Miss Smith doesn’t have ______ housework to do today.\nA. much  B. many  C. a lot  D. a piece\n( A ) 5) We finally got several ______ of his innocence.\nA. proof  B. proofs  C. proves  D. prooves\n( D ) 6) A group of boy students ______ basketball on the playground at the moment.\nA. play  B. plays  C. is playing  D. are playing\n( C ) 7) My aunt bought ______ cotton stockings for me at the department store.\nA. a pair of  B. a loaf of  C. a piece of  D. a group of\n( B ) 8) Wang Daming has caught some ______, and his family will have ______ for supper today.\nA. fish … fishes  B. fishes … fish  C. fishes … fishes  D. fishing … fish\n( D ) 9) There are many ______ in this hospital.\nA. woman doctor  B. woman doctors  C. women doctor  D. women doctors\n( D ) 10) Last week I ate ______.\nA. too much hamburger  B. too many hamburger  C. too many hamburgers  D. too much hamburgers\niii. 不可数名词\n选择填空。\n( D ) 1) There was ______ mud on the ground after the heavy rain.",
